{"tid":12433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宅男玉蓮臺上吊亡 母親哭訴︰畀電話、網絡搞死","createTime":"2016-11-29T16:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T16:26:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2121e803d20b2cd106f9a16578b2013359540e8c","tid":12433,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:00:56.000Z","msg":"牛頭角一名隱閉青年昨晚被母親發現在寓所上吊身亡（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2fGlr4Y），警方在現場未有撿獲遺書，初步相信案件無可疑。母親事後忍喪子之痛表示：「以前冇隱閉青年㗎，唔會匿喺屋企，依家啲人全部畀電話、網絡搞死咗。」，她呼籲其他家長要主動與子女多溝通。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2fGlr4Y%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9C%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E6%92%BF%E7%8D%B2%E9%81%BA%E6%9B%B8%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E6%A1%88%E4%BB%B6%E7%84%A1%E5%8F%AF%E7%96%91%E3%80%82%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E4%BA%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%BF%8D%E5%96%AA%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%8B%E7%97%9B%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%89%8D%E5%86%87%E9%9A%B1%E9%96%89%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E3%97%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%94%94%E6%9C%83%E5%8C%BF%E5%96%BA%E5%B1%8B%E4%BC%81%EF%BC%8C%E4%BE%9D%E5%AE%B6%E5%95%B2%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%95%80%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%81%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E6%90%9E%E6%AD%BB%E5%92%97%E3%80%82%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%A5%B9%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%88%87%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%9A%E6%BA%9D%E9%80%9A%E3%80%82&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=afb633a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2fGlr4Y），警方在現場未有撿獲遺書，初步相信案件無可疑。母親事後忍喪子之痛表示：「以前冇隱閉青年㗎，唔會匿喺屋企，依家啲人全部畀電話、網絡搞死咗。」，她呼籲其他家長要主動與子女多溝通。</a> <br />\n<br />\n自縊身亡青年姓李（25歲），與父母及胞妹，住牛頭角花園大廈玉蓮臺2座一單位。據悉，李中五畢業後，一直沒有工作，常年足不出戶，是隱閉青年，其父親於年初病逝，母親從事夜更工作。現場所見其家門外貼有一張一家四口的圖畫，但一年內父子均離逝，街坊不勝欷歔。 <br />\n<br />\n昨晚10時許，52歲姓吳母親回家時，驚見兒子在屋內用繩上吊自殺，連忙報案，惟救護員到場證實表年已身，吳婦傷心欲絕，她今午接受訪問時稱：「以前冇隱閉青年㗎，唔會匿喺屋企，全部畀手機、網絡搞死咗。」她更強忍喪子之痛表示會堅強面對：「凡事應該由正面出發，積極去處理事情，唔好抱怨，唔好問點解，好多嘢無得點解」，又呼籲其他家長，要主動與子女多溝通。 <br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰ <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000 <br />\n生命熱線︰23820000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281 <br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255 <br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350 <br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161129/55979871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161129%2F55979871&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=56bf1e36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161129%2F55979871&h=f4a67046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161129/55979871</a>"},{"pid":"3a8fdaf04192f5bcabb26e7d9b40cd348ab1ddda","tid":12433,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:02:19.000Z","msg":"毒男<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffea5d68d21cc5ff3297af99522245182c0e240","tid":12433,"uid":20117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:04:23.000Z","msg":"最近越來越多後生走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw rip"},{"pid":"93f21d7acae426539107756c293d7b2dddf75ab4","tid":12433,"uid":14217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:05:48.000Z","msg":"我好快就會係下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d1e09b48e6f16f79f57ca7b24592c18949493b","tid":12433,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:14:25.000Z","msg":"以前個社會夠冇咁複雜，一個人做嘢養得起成家有凸，又唔見你講"},{"pid":"8358a9aabda531e40b310ec447a8bf8c4a528790","tid":12433,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9320b8bf94368cda7da995907eab154414b24ce8","tid":12433,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:19:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好快就會係